'Phendimetrazine' ('Bontril', 'Adipost', 'Anorex-SR', 'Appecon', 'Melfiat',
'Obezine', 'Phendiet', 'Plegine', 'Prelu-2', 'Statobex') is a stimulant drug of
the morpholine chemical class used as an appetite suppressant.
